# Ticket #4 – DNS Issue

## Issue:
The user is unable to access company resources

## Investigation:
Opened Active Directory and the client computer
Used NSLookup to verify domain controller DNS resolution
Verified that the domain controller could not be reached
Checked the DNS settings for the user computer

## Root Cause:
The users IPV4 DNS settings were incorrect

## Resolution:
I set the IPV4 DNS to the correct settings
Used NSLookup to ping the domain controller

## Verification:
The user computer successfully pinged the domain controller
